    "description": "布袋英雄》（Ragtag Heroes）是一款最多可由 3 名玩家合作的轻流氓卡组制作游戏！<br>制作自己的卡组，在策略战斗中击败强大的敌人，收集稀有卡牌和遗物，一起拯救王国！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>控制战场</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/ec269e8e0e8c5fb2c4364d4c3b0d10c5.poster.avif?t=1770831788\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/ec269e8e0e8c5fb2c4364d4c3b0d10c5.webm?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/ec269e8e0e8c5fb2c4364d4c3b0d10c5.mp4?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>将进攻的怪物推离虚弱的英雄，让你的近战攻击者近距离给予致命一击。<br>将怪物锁定在原地或惩罚它们四处移动，但要小心它们可能会对你做出同样的举动！<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >跨卡组协同作战！</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/abe563efe545cf8ec71afef46e0b4fa7.poster.avif?t=1770831788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/abe563efe545cf8ec71afef46e0b4fa7.webm?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/abe563efe545cf8ec71afef46e0b4fa7.mp4?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br><br>每个英雄都有自己的优缺点，因此在构建卡组时可以采用多种策略。他们与其他英雄的协同作用也各不相同--因此通过更换队友，您可以在每次运行时探索不同的团队战术。<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握主动权！</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/60b9f4d15a1e66bdce189fdecf632e79.poster.avif?t=1770831788\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/60b9f4d15a1e66bdce189fdecf632e79.webm?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/60b9f4d15a1e66bdce189fdecf632e79.mp4?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>主动权<br><br>主动权决定了战斗中的回合顺序。战略性地降低对手的主动权可以让你的英雄更快地行动。<br>您甚至可以集中精力将一个敌人的主动权降为零，使其眩晕，从而迫使他们跳过一个回合。<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >控制你的能量流!</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/daeb611d10d5982f11a45b104f38a60e.poster.avif?t=1770831788\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/daeb611d10d5982f11a45b104f38a60e.webm?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/daeb611d10d5982f11a45b104f38a60e.mp4?t=1770831788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br><br>勇敢 &quot;和 &quot;默认 &quot;为您的战略添加了额外的一层。<br>&quot;勇敢 &quot;会为您当前的回合提供更多能量，但您会被眩晕，不得不放弃下一个回合。<br>或者 &quot;默认 &quot;您的回合而不执行任何操作，您将在剩余的战斗中为您的英雄增加 1 的能量。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067070/extras/371537f95fe9aab688b4eb9ccf930c16.avif?t=1770831788\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br><br>[list］<br>[4 个以上英雄拥有自己的卡牌组合<br>[300 多张不同的卡牌<br>[100 多种可找到的物品<br>[50 多种独特的战斗遭遇<br>[40 多种神秘的故事情节<br>[本地和在线多人合作游戏，最多可容纳 3 名玩家<br>[/list］",
